<p>bombed the pond for fish.</p>
<p>Arthur brought me some letters this morning &amp; showed me some responses to some nice things I had been saying about him (merely truth if I remember rightly) by his cousin who gained it from the [indecipherable].  Also there were references of a complementary nature both to him &amp; me.</p>
<p>He told me all about the line up at Strazeele &amp; Bone, &amp; it seems even better than Meteren.</p>
